areer%2C%20BLR%20is%20the%20place%20with%20the%20highest%20probability!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20stated%2C%20''Its%20robust%20infrastructure%2C%20talent%20pool%2C%20and%20cosmopolitan%20culture%20foster%20innovation.%20The%20city's%20pro-business%20policies%20and%20vibrant%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%20make%20it%20an%20ideal%20launchpad%20for%20new%20ventures.%20Moreover%2C%20its%20pleasant%20weather%20throughout%20the%20year%20aids%20productivity.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20fourth%20user%20said%2C%20''Opposite%20situation%20here%2C%20everyone%20I%20know%20wants%20to%20get%20out%20of%20Bangalore.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It's%20digital%20era%20why%20not%20move%20out%20engineer%20talent%20out%20to%20peaceful%20tier%202%20city%20where%20they%20can%20get%20better%20and%20cheap%20food%20and%20stay.%20Keep%20marketing%2Fsales%20team%20in%20such%20cities%3F''%2C%20added%20a%20fifth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20disagreed%20saying%2C%20''Literally%20the%20worst.%20Only%20gud%20if%20u%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Extremely%20high%20rent%2C%20water%20issues%2C%20transport%20issues.%20If%20u%20r%20not%20living%20in%20prime%20areas%20then%20be%20prepared%20to%20get%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20fr%20hrs%20where%20the%20cab%20driver%20won't%20even%20turn%20on%20the%20AC%20%2B%20only%20god%20can%20hlp%20u%20when%20it%20starts%20raining.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20he%20has%20praised%20the%20city.%20He%20had%20previously%20urged%20entrepreneurs%20to%20come%20to%20Bengaluru%20if%20they%20were%20serious%20about%20making%20it%20big%20in%20the%20startup%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717393740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ftsjdgd9o_unacademy-ceo-gaurav-munjal_625x300_12_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Funacademy-ceo-gaurav-munjal-calls-bengaluru-best-city-in-india-divides-the-internet-5804832%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20said%20tha