rters%20of%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20both%20Uddhav%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20earned%20some%20sympathy%20from%20the%20public%20as%20they%20lost%20official%20symbols%20to%20rival%20groups.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20expects%20to%20defeat%20the%20NDA%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20battles.%20The%20poll%20of%20polls%20suggests%20that%20they%20might%20even%20have%20succeeded%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20though%20the%20national%20character%20of%20the%20elections%20and%20the%20popularity%20of%20Modi%20have%20helped%20the%20BJP%20rein%20in%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvantage%20BJP%20In%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20NDA%20won%2018%20out%20of%2042%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20fighting%20separately%20then%2C%20had%20got%2024%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20are%20not%20in%20an%20alliance%20this%20time%20as%20well%2C%20though%20Mamata%20claims%20to%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Here%2C%20polls%20estimate%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20gain%20five%20seats%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Trinamool.%20This%20could%20be%20due%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20Trinamool's%20women%20support%20after%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident%2C%20polarisation%20due%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20new%20citizenship%20rules%2C%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%2013-year-old%20Mamata%20government%2C%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSP%20May%20Play%20Spoiler%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20won%2064%20of%20the%2080%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202019%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20fighting%20separately%20then%2C%20won%20six.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20then%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%2C%20