here.%20I'm%20very%20sensitive%20to%20vibes%2C%20and%20this%20place%20gives%20me%20positive%20ones.%20Our%20homes%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Mumbai%20have%20been%20surrounded%20by%20trees%20and%20we%20used%20to%20feed%20birds%20and%20squirrels.%20So%2C%20I%20wanted%20a%20home%20with%20a%20view%20and%20ample%20space%20to%20feed%20birds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActress%20Adah%20Sharma%20was%20seen%20outside%20late%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20apartment%20last%20year.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20about%20whether%20she%20is%20buying%20the%20flat%20that%20the%20actor%20stayed%20at%2C%20before%20his%20death.%20Earlier%2C%20when%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20same%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20Siddharth%20Kannan%2C%20the%20actress%20mentioned%20that%20when%20she%20went%20to%20see%20the%20apartment%2C%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Coverwhelmed%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20media%20attention.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20now%20I%20would%20just%20like%20to%20say%20that%20I%20live%20in%20everyone's%20hearts.%20There%20is%20a%20right%20time%20to%20speak.%20When%20I%20had%20gone%20to%20see%20the%20place%2C%20I%20got%20a%20little%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20media%20attention.%20I%20am%20a%20private%20person.%20I%20love%20being%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20for%20my%20movies%2C%20but%20I%20have%20always%20been%20private.%20I%20guard%20my%20privacy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20June%2014%2C%202020%2C%20in%20his%20Mumbai%20apartment.%20He%20was%2034.%20The%20actor%20has%20given%20Bollywood%20many%20hit%20films%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EChhichhore%2C%20M.S.%20Dhoni%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story%2C%20and%20Kai%20Po%20Che!%3C%2Fem%3E%20Sushant's%20last%20movie%2C%3Cem%3E%20Dil%20Bechara%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20released%20posthumously.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Adah%20Sharma%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20Sudipto%20Sen's%20%3Cem%3EBastar%3A%20The%20Naxal%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ