nsington%20Oval.%20Ruben%20Trumpelmann's%20historic%20feat%20of%20two%20wickets%20in%20two%20balls%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20Namibia's%20disciplined%20bowling%20display.%20Jan%20Frylinck's%20steady%2045%20and%20a%20resilient%20Super%20Over%20sealed%20the%20victory%20for%20Namibia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Russia%20now%20is%20like%201984'%3A%20Inside%20a%20Russian%20dystopian%20library%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717390026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0dd4%2Flive%2F82b5d620-1dd1-11ef-80aa-699d54c46324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckrr1k1xl0lo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deep%20in%20Putin's%20Russia%2C%20Ivanovo's%20George%20Orwell%20library%20is%20still%20lending%20books%20on%20totalitarianism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckrr1k1xl0lo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckrr1k1xl0lo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckrr1k1xl0lo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20New%20Resolve%20After%2045-Hour%20Meditation%20In%20Kanniyakumari%3A%20Full%20Text%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20concluded%20a%2045-hour%20meditation%20at%20the%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Kanniyakumari.%20PM%20Modi's%20meditation%20began%20on%20May%2030%20and%20continued%20till%20June%201%2C%20for%20nearly%2045%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20meditation%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20reflect%20on%20his%20spiritual%20journey%2C%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20India's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20text%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20letter%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Sankalps%20from%20the%20Sadhana%20in%20Kanniyakumari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20fellow%20Indians%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20festival%20of%20democracy%2C%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%2C%20are%20concluding%20today%20in%20our%20nation%2C%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy.%20After%20a%20three-day%20spiritual%20journey%20in%20Kanniyakumari%2C%20I%20have%20just%20boarded%20the%20plane%20for%20Delhi.%20Through%20the%20day%2C%20Kashi%20and%20numerous%20other%20seats%20have%20been%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20mind%20is%20filled%20with%20so%20many%20experiences%20and%20emotions...%20I%20feel%20a%20boundless%20flow%20of%20energy%20within%20myself.%20The%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20the%20first%20in%20the%20Amrit%20Kaal.%20I%20began%20my%20campaign%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20from%20Meerut%2C%20the%20land%20of%20the%20First%20War%20of%20Independence%20of%201857.%20Since%20then%2C%20I%20have%20traversed%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20our%20great%20nation.%20The%20final%20rally%20of%20these%20elections%20took%20me%20to%20Hoshiarpur%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20land%20of%20the%20great%20Gurus%20and%20a%20land%20associated%20with%20Sant%20Ravidas%20Ji.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20came%20to%20Kanniyakumari%2C%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20Maa%20Bharti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20natural%20that%20the%20fervour%20of%20the%20elections%20was%20echoing%20in%20my%20heart%20and%20mind.%20The%20multitude%20of%20faces%20seen%20in%20rallies%20and%20road%20shows%20came%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes.%20The%20blessings%20from%20our%20Nari%20Shakti...the%20trust%2C%20the%20affection%2C%20all%20of%20this%20was%20a%20very%20humbling%20experience.%20My%20eyes%20were%20getting%20moist...%20I%20entered%20into%20a%20'sadhana'%20(meditative%20state).%20And%20then%2C%20the%20heated%20political%20debates%2C%20the%20attacks%20and%20counter-attacks%2C%20the%20voices%20and%20words%20of%20accusations%20which%20are%20so%20characteristic%20of%20an%20election...they%20all%20vanished%20into%20a%20void.%20A%20sense%20of%20detachment%20came%20to%20grow%20within%20me...my%20mind%20became%20completely%20detached%20from%20the%20external%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeditation%20becomes%20challenging%20amidst%20such%20huge%20responsibilities%2C%20but%20the%20land%20of%20Kanniyakumari%20and%20the%20inspiration%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20made%20it%20effortless.%20As%20a%20candidate%20myself%2C%20I%20left%20my%20campaign%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20my%20beloved%20people%20of%20Kashi%20and%20came%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20also%20grateful%20God%20for%20instilling%20me%20with%20these%20values%20from%20birth%20which%20I%20have%20cherished%20and%20tried%20to%20live%20up%20to.%20I%20was%20also%20thinking%20about%20what%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20must%20have%20experienced%20during%20his%20meditation%20at%20this%20very%20place%20in%20Kanniyakumari!%20A%20part%20of%20my%20meditation%20was%20spent%20in%20a%20similar%20stream%20of%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20detachment%2C%20amidst%20the%20peace%20and%20silence%2C%20my%20mind%20was%20constantly%20thinking%20about%20the%20bright%20future%20of%20Bharat%2C%20the%20goals%20of%20Bharat.%20The%20rising%20sun%20at%20Kanniyakumari%20gave%20new%20heights%20to%20my%20thoughts%2C%20the%20vastness%20of%20the%20ocean%20expanded%20my%20ideas%2C%20and%20the%20expanse%20of%20the%20horizon%20continuously%20made%20me%20realize%20the%20unity%2C%20the%20Oneness%2C%20embedded%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20universe.%20It%20seemed%20as%20if%20the%20observations%20and%20experiences%20undertaken%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20decades%20ago%20were%20being%20revived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriends%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanniyakumari%20has%20always%20been%20very%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%20The%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20in%20Kanniyakumari%20was%20built%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Shri%20Eknath%20Ranade%20ji.%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20extensively%20with%20Eknath%20ji.%20During%20the%20construction%20of%20this%20Memorial%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20in%20Kanniyakumari%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Kashmir%20to%20Kanniyakumari...%20this%20is%20a%20common%20identity%20that%20is%20deeply%20ingrained%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20citizen%20of%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20the%20'Shakti%20Peeth'%20(seat%20of%20Shakti)%20where%20Maa%20Shakti%20incarnated%20as%20Kanya%20Kumari.%20At%20this%20Southern%20tip%2C%20Maa%20Shakti%20performed%20penance%20and%20waited%20for%20Bhagwan%20Shiva%2C%20who%20was%20residing%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20at%20the%20northernmost%20parts%20of%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanniyakumari%20is%20the%20land%20of%20confluences.%20The%20sacred%20rivers%20of%20our%20country%20flow%20into%20different%20seas%2C%20and%20here%2C%20those%20very%20seas%20converge.%20And%20here%2C%20we%20witness%20another%20great%20confluence-the%20ideological%20confluence%20of%20Bharat!%20Here%2C%20we%20find%20the%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%2C%20a%20grand%20statue%20of%20Saint%20Thiruvalluvar%2C%20Gandhi%20Mandapam%2C%20and%20Kamarajar%20Mani%20Mandapam.%20These%20streams%20of%20thought%20from%20these%20stalwarts%20converge%20here%20to%20form%20a%20confluence%20of%20national%20thought.%20This%20gives%20rise%20to%20great%20inspirations%20for%20nation-building.%20This%20land%20of%20Kanniyakumari%20gives%20an%20indelible%20message%20of%20unity%2C%20especially%20to%20any%20person%20who%20doubts%20Bharat's%20nationhood%20and%20the%20sense%20of%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grand%20statue%20of%20Saint%20Thiruvalluvar%20in%20Kanniyakumari%20seems%20to%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20expanse%20of%20Maa%20Bharati%20from%20the%20sea.%20His%20work%20Thirukkural%20is%20one%20of%20the%20crown%20jewels%20of%20the%20beautiful%20Tamil%20language.%20It%20covers%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%2C%20inspiring%20us%20to%20give%20our%20best%20for%20ourselves%20and%20for%20the%20nation.%20It%20was%20my%20great%20fortune%20to%20pay%20my%20respects%20to%20such%20a%20great%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriends%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Vivekananda%20once%20said%2C%20'Every%20nation%20has%20a%20message%20to%20deliver%2C%20a%20mission%20to%20fulfil%2C%20a%20destiny%20to%20reach.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20Bharat%20has%20been%20moving%20forward%20with%20this%20sense%20of%20meaningful%20purpose.%20Bharat%20has%20been%20a%20cradle%20of%20ideas%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20We%20have%20never%20considered%20what%20we%20have%20acquired%20as%20our%20personal%20wealth%20or%20measured%20it%20purely%20by%20economic%20or%20material%20parameters.%20Therefore%2C%20'Idam-na-mama'%20(this%20is%20not%20mine)%20has%20become%20an%20inherent%20and%20natural%20part%20of%20the%20character%20of%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat's%20welfare%20benefits%20our%20planet's%20journey%20to%20progress%20as%20well.%20Take%20the%20freedom%20movement%20as%20an%20example.%20Bharat%20gained%20independence%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20many%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20were%20under%20colonial%20rule.%20Bharat's%20independence%20journey%20inspired%20and%20empowered%20many%20of%20those%20countries%20to%20achieve%20their%20own%20freedom.%20That%20same%20spirit%20was%20seen%20decades%20later%20when%20the%20world%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20once%20in%20a%20century%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20When%20concerns%20were%20raised%20about%20the%20poor%20and%20developing%20countries%2C%20Bharat's%20successful%20efforts%20provided%20courage%20and%20assistance%20to%20many%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bharat's%20governance%20model%20has%20become%20an%20example%20for%20many%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%20Empowering%2025%20crore%20people%20to%20rise%20above%20poverty%20in%20just%2010%20years%20is%20unprecedented.%20Innovative%20practices%20such%20as%20Pro-People%20Good%20Governance%2C%20aspirational%20districts%2C%20and%20aspirational%20blocks%20are%20being%20discussed%20globally%20today.%20Our%20efforts%2C%20from%20empowering%20the%20poor%20to%20last-mile%20delivery%2C%20have%20inspired%20the%20world%20by%20prioritizing%20individuals%20standing%20at%20the%20last%20rung%20of%20society.%20Bharat's%20Digital%20India%20campaign%20is%20now%20an%20example%20for%20the%20entire%20world%2C%20showing%20how%20we%20can%20use%20technology%20to%20empower%20the%20poor%2C%20bring%20transparency%2C%20and%20ensure%20their%20rights.%20Inexpensive%20data%20in%20Bharat%20is%20becoming%20a%20means%20of%20social%20equality%20by%20ensuring%20the%20reach%20of%20information%20and%20services%20to%20the%20poor.%20The%20whole%20world%20is%20witnessing%20and%20studying%20the%20democratization%20of%20technology%2C%20and%20major%20global%20institutions%20are%20advising%20many%20countries%20to%20adopt%20elements%20from%20our%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bharat's%20progress%20and%20rise%20are%20not%20just%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20for%20Bharat%20alone%2C%20but%20also%20a%20historic%20opportunity%20for%20all%20our%20partner%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%20Since%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G-20%2C%20the%20world%20has%20been%20increasingly%20envisioning%20a%20bigger%20role%20for%20Bharat.%20Today%2C%20Bharat%20is%20being%20acknowledged%20as%20a%20strong%20and%20important%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%20The%20African%20Union%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20G-20%20group%20at%20the%20initiative%20of%20Bharat.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20crucial%20turning%20point%20for%20the%20future%20of%20African%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriends%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20trajectory%20of%20Bharat%20fills%20us%20with%20pride%20and%20glory%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20also%20reminds%20the%20140%20crore%20citizens%20of%20their%20responsibilities.%20Now%2C%20without%20wasting%20a%20single%20moment%2C%20we%20must%20step%20forward%20towards%20greater%20duties%20and%20larger%20goals.%20We%20need%20to%20dream%20new%20dreams%2C%20convert%20them%20into%20reality%20and%20begin%20living%20those%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20see%20Bharat's%20development%20in%20a%20global%20context%2C%20and%20for%20this%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20that%20we%20understand%20Bharat's%20internal%20capabilities.%20We%20must%20acknowledge%20Bharat's%20strengths%2C%20nurture%20them%2C%20and%20utilize%20them%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20world.%20In%20today's%20global%20scenario%2C%20Bharat's%20strength%20as%20a%20youthful%20nation%20is%20an%20opportunity%20from%20which%20we%20must%20not%20look%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20is%20looking%20towards%20Bharat%20with%20many%20hopes.%20And%20we%20will%20need%20to%20make%20several%20changes%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20the%20global%20scenario.%20We%20also%20need%20to%20change%20our%20traditional%20thinking%20regarding%20reform.%20Bharat%20cannot%20limit%20reform%20to%20just%20economic%20reforms.%20We%20must%20move%20forward%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%20towards%20the%20direction%20of%20reform.%20Our%20reforms%20should%20also%20align%20with%20the%20aspirations%20of%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20(developed%20India)%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20also%20understand%20that%20reform%20can%20never%20be%20a%20unidimensional%20process%20for%20any%20country.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20have%20laid%20out%20the%20vision%20of%20reform%2C%20perform%2C%20and%20transform%20for%20the%20country.%20The%20responsibility%20of%20reform%20lies%20with%20leadership.%20Based%20on%20that%2C%20our%20bureaucracy%20performs%2C%20and%20when%20the%20people%20join%20in%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20Jan%20Bhagidari%2C%20we%20witness%20a%20transformation%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20make%20excellence%20the%20fundamental%20principle%20to%20make%20our%20country%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%20We%20need%20to%20work%20quickly%20in%20all%20four%20directions%3A%20Speed%2C%20Scale%2C%20Scope%2C%20and%20Standards.%20Alongside%20manufacturing%2C%20we%20must%20also%20focus%20on%20quality%20and%20adhere%20to%20the%20mantra%20of%20'zero%20defect-zero%20effect'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriends%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20should%20take%20pride%20in%20every%20moment%20that%20God%20has%20blessed%20us%20with%20birth%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Bharat.%20God%20has%20chosen%20us%20to%20serve%20Bharat%20and%20fulfil%20our%20role%20in%20our%20country's%20journey%20towards%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20redefine%20our%20heritage%20in%20a%20modern%20way%20while%20embracing%20ancient%20values%20in%20a%20modern%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20also%20need%20to%20reassess%20outdated%20thinking%20and%20beliefs.%20We%20need%20to%20free%20our%20society%20from%20the%20pressure%20of%20professional%20pessimists.%20We%20must%20remember%20that%20freedom%20from%20negativity%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20achieving%20success.%20Success%20blossoms%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20positivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20faith%2C%20devotion%2C%20and%20belief%20in%20the%20infinite%20and%20eternal%20power%20of%20Bharat%20are%20growing%20day%20by%20day.%20Over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20this%20capability%20of%20Bharat%20grow%20even%20more%20and%20have%20experienced%20it%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20we%20utilized%20the%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20decades%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20to%20impart%20a%20new%20momentum%20to%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20we%20must%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20in%20these%2025%20years%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20The%20freedom%20struggle%20was%20a%20time%20that%20called%20for%20great%20sacrifices.%20The%20present%20times%20call%20for%20great%20and%20sustained%20contributions%20from%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Vivekananda%20had%20said%20in%201897%20that%20we%20must%20dedicate%20the%20next%2050%20years%20solely%20for%20the%20nation.%20Exactly%2050%20years%20after%20this%20call%2C%20Bharat%20gained%20independence%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20have%20the%20same%20golden%20opportunity.%20Let's%20dedicate%20the%20next%2025%20years%20solely%20for%20the%20nation.%20Our%20efforts%20will%20create%20a%20strong%20foundation%20for%20the%20coming%20generations%20and%20the%20coming%20centuries%2C%20taking%20Bharat%20to%20new%20heights.%20Looking%20at%20the%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm%20of%20the%20country%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20the%20goal%20is%20not%20far%20away%20now.%20Let%20us%20take%20swift%20steps...let%20us%20come%20together%20and%20create%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EThese%20thoughts%20were%20penned%20by%20PM%20Modi%20on%201st%20June%20between%204%3A15%20PM%20and%207%20PM%20during%20his%20return%20flight%20from%20Kanniyakumari%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717389780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F2c4h1tuo_pm-modi_625x300_01_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-pens-his-thoughts-on-indias-future-after-45-hour-meditation-full-text-5804299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20concluded%20a%2045-hour%20meditation%20at%20the%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Kanniyakumari.%20PM%20Modi's%20meditation%20began%20on%20May%2030%20and%20continued%20till%20June%201%2C%20for%20nearly%2045%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-pens-his-thoughts-on-indias-future-after-45-hour-meditation-full-text-5804299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-co