dia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fworld-cup-jeetwa-ke-dain-ahmed-shehzad-challenges-babar-azam-watch%2Farticleshow%2F110653366.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20cricketers%20face%20criticism%20at%20home%20ahead%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Ahmed%20Shehzad%20challenges%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20to%20win%202024%20edition.%20Former%20PCB%20chairman%20Ramiz%20Raja%20criticized%20team%20after%20T20I%20series%20loss%20to%20England.%20Led%20by%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20coached%20by%20Gary%20Kirtsen%2C%20Pakistan%20are%20scheduled%20to%20open%20their%20campaign%20against%20USA%20on%20Thursday%20and%20will%20clash%20with%20India%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fworld-cup-jeetwa-ke-dain-ahmed-shehzad-challenges-babar-azam-watch%2Farticleshow%2F110653366.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Billionaire%20CEO's%20Wealth%20Dropped%20By%20%2411.7%20Billion%20In%20A%20Single%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMichael%20Dell%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20computer%20manufacturer%20Dell%20Technologies%2C%20experienced%20the%20largest%20single-day%20decline%20in%20his%20wealth%20due%20to%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%C2%A0Dell%20shares.%C2%A0Dell's%20net%20worth%20dropped%20%2411.7%20billion%20to%20%24107.1%20billion%20on%20Friday%20as%20shares%20of%20Dell%20Technologies%20Inc.%20fell%2018%25%20in%20New%20York%2C%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20reported%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDell%20is%20on%20track%20to%20lose%20more%20than%20USD%2021%20billion%20in%20market%20value%20if%20losses%20hold.%C2%A0The%20drop%20in%20Dell's%20stock%20came%20after%20investors%20were%20discouraged%20by%20the%20company's%20lower-than-expected%20artificial%20intelligence%20server%20backlog%20and%20an%20estimated%20decline%20in%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20decline%2C%20the%2059-year-old%20tech%20billionaire%20now%20ranks%2013th%20on%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%C2%A0%24107.1%20billion.%20Notably%2C%20Mr%20Dell's%20wealth%20primarily%20comes%20from%20Dell%20Technologies%20Inc.%2C%20a%20company%20he%20started%20over%2040%20years%20ago%20while%20studying%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas.%20Another%20major%20source%20of%20his%20net%20worth%20comes%20from%20his%20stake%20in%20Broadcom%20Inc.%2C%20whose%20shares%20also%20slid%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20March%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20exclusive%20group%20of%20individuals%20with%20fortunes%20exceeding%20%24100%20billion%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20increasing%20demand%20for%20AI%20computing%20equipment%2C%20which%20pushed%20Dell's%20shares%20to%20a%20record%20high.%20Large%20corporations%20increasingly%20need%20high-powered%20servers%20to%20train%20and%20run%20demanding%20generative%20AI%20tasks%2C%20which%20are%20sold%20by%20Dell%20and%20a%20few%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F05%2F30%2Fdell-earnings-q1-2025.html%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dell%20reported%20first-quarter%20earnings%20on%20Thursday%20that%20beat%20analysts'%20estimates%20for%20earnings%20and%20sales%2C%20as%20the%20company%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20vendors%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20servers.%20However%2C%20its%20shares%20fell%20more%20than%2015%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20on%20concerns%20Dell's%20AI%20servers%20aren't%20making%20the%20company%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Thursday's%20report%2C%20Dell%20shares%20had%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Relative%20to%20very%20high%20expectations%2C%20Dell's%20Q1%2025%20results%20were%20disappointing%2C''%20Toni%20Sacconaghi%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Sanford%20Bernstein%20sa