20of%20the%20results%20pending%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aggregate%20of%2012%20exit%20polls%20on%20Saturday%20predicted%20the%20BJP%20will%20return%20to%20power%20with%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20alliance%20with%20365%20seats.%20A%20party%20or%20an%20alliance%20needs%20at%20least%20272%20seats%20to%20form%20government%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20market%20prefers%20political%20stability%20and%20a%20change%20in%20government%20usually%20risks%20volatility%20in%20the%20share%20market%2C%20according%20to%20analysts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exit%20polls%20have%20also%20predicted%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20to%20break%20ground%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20south%2C%20and%20make%20large%20gains%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Bengal%20in%20the%20east.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20health%20warning%3A%20exit%20polls%20do%20not%20always%20get%20it%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20the%20exit%20poll%20predictions%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20dismissed%20the%20forecast%20and%20said%20the%20counting%20day%20will%20throw%20a%20completely%20different%20picture.%20Following%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Saturday%20said%20that%20the%20bloc%20will%20win%20at%20least%20295%20seats%20out%20of%20the%20total%20543%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717388760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fl8lra8j_bse-generic-share-market-generic-sensex-generic-pti_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-jump-in-stock-market-after-exit-polls-predict-big-bjp-win-5804282%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20share%20market%20has%20posted%20a%20massive%20jump%20in%20the%20early%20trade%2C%20banking%20on%20the%20hopes%20of%20political%20stability%20as%20predicted%20by%20the%20exit%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr