20science%20and%20AI%20at%20Air%20France-KLM%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%2080th%20meeting%20of%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association%20(IATA)%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirline%20executives%20will%20gather%20at%20the%20influential%20annual%20global%20airline%20summit%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20on%20Monday%20for%20talks%20on%20the%20latest%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20including%20upcoming%20AI%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAviation%20companies%2C%20long%20accustomed%20to%20thin%20profit%20margins%2C%20see%20AI%20as%20the%20newest%20way%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20gain%20a%20competitive%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20%26quot%3Bundoubtedly%20a%20new%20frontier%2C%20in%20that%20it's%20an%20extraordinary%20acceleration%20of%20technology%20and%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Geoffrey%20Weston%2C%20the%20head%20consultant%20on%20the%20airline%20industry%20at%20US-based%20firm%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty...%20what%20AI%20is%20really%20helpful%20for%20is%20to%20hugely%20accelerate%20getting%20the%20right%20information%20to%20the%20right%20people%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20France-KLM%20is%20doing%20this%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%2040%20projects%20using%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20like%20the%20now-famous%20ChatGPT%20is%20meant%20to%20improve%20as%20it%20is%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20French-Dutch%20company's%20plans%20is%20a%20tool%20that%20responds%20to%20customers%20in%2085%20different%20languages.%20It%20will%20be%20installed%20on%20the%20tablets%20of%20Air%20France%20agents%20and%20is%20scheduled%20for%20use%20in%202025%20at%20Paris%20Charles%20de%20Gaulle%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'%3Cstrong%3EAssisted%20intelligence'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport's%20operator%2C%20Groupe%20ADP%2C%20has%20also%20launched%20several%20AI%20initiatives%20in%20cooperation%20with%20startups%20--%20including%20Allobrain%2C%20which%20uses%20voice%20recognition%20to%20answer%20phone%20calls%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20reduced%20%26quot%3Bthe%20number%20of%20unanswered%20phone%20calls%20from%2050%20per%20cent%20to%2010%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alban%20Negret%2C%20the%20head%20of%20ADP's%20innovation%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20operator%20hopes%20to%20streamline%20drop-off%20areas%20and%20shuttle%20rotations%20through%20the%20help%20of%20another%20subcontractor%2C%20Wintics%2C%20which%20specialises%20in%20extracting%20data%20from%20real-time%20surveillance%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20air%20travel%20grows%2C%20reducing%20wait%20times%20is%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20important%20challenges%2C%20according%20to%20aerospace%20expert%20Jerome%20Bouchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20and%20more%20passengers%20in%20increasingly%20constrained%20spaces%2C%20and%20we%20are%20still%20travelling%20as%20we%20did%20in%20the%201970s%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20consultant%20for%20Oliver%20Wyman's%20Transportation%20and%20Services%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20room%20for%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20using%20facial%20recognition%20at%20airport%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20all%20this%20requires%20enormous%20coordination%20and%20data%20synchronisation%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20still%20lacking%2C%20according%20to%20Bouchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModern%20aircraft%2C%20with%20their%20sophisticated%20self-diagnostic%20and%20control%20systems%2C%20are%20data%20factories%20that%20can%20be%20leveraged%20with%20AI%2C%20the%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20actually%20piloting%20the%20aircraft%2C%20they%20say%20there%20is%20no%20question%20about%20leaving%20it%20to%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20