2%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsouth-africa-election-result-confirms-no-party-won-a-majority-alliance-talks-start%2Farticleshow%2F110649376.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsouth-africa-election-result-confirms-no-party-won-a-majority-alliance-talks-start%2Famp_articleshow%2F110649376.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsouth-africa-election-result-confirms-no-party-won-a-majority-alliance-talks-start%2Famp_articleshow%2F110649376.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20MBAs%20are%20flocking%20to%20search%20funds.%20One%20Harvard%20grad%20explained%20why%20he%20founded%20a%20%24600%2C000%20fund%20to%20buy%20tech%20companies.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20Singh%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665432d0239fda2da6cbde9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGaurav%20Singh%20launched%20his%20own%20search%20fund%20earlier%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EGaurav%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGaurav%20Singh%20founded%20a%20fund%20to%20buy%20software%20companies%20after%20his%20Harvard%20MBA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shifted%20to%20search%20funds%20after%20struggling%20to%20gain%20traction%20with%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESingh%20thought%20the%20search%20fund%20offered%20a%20path%20to%20leadership%20and%20flexibility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20MBA%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20Gaurav%20Singh%20pursued%20a%20tennis%20coaching%20app%20that%20didn't%20gain%20much%20traction%20with%20venture%20capitalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20ultimately%20failed%2C%20and%20after%20graduation%2C%20he%20worked%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20at%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20startup%20in%20Toronto%20before%20exploring%20other%20avenues.%20He%20landed%20on%20an%20option%20that's%20becoming%20increasingly%20popular%20with%20top%20MBAs%20and%20entrepreneurs%3A%20launching%20his%20own%20search%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Singh%2C%2031%2C%20founded%20Guddi%20Growth.%20The%20Toronto-based%20search%20fund%20focuses%20on%20buying%20software-as-a-service%20companies%20with%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20of%20at%20least%20%245%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a04e0ee0-c77f-4845-9cff-fb8684d52c52%5C%22%3ELower%20salary%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20big%20potential%20payday%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20search%20fund%20founder%20like%20Singh%20raises%20money%20from%20investors%20to%20buy%20and%20operate%20a%20privately%20held%20business%2C%20like%20manufacturing%2C%20home%20improvement%2C%20and%20transportation%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20put%20%242.3%20billion%20in%20search%20funds%20between%201986%20and%202021%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsb.stanford.edu%2Fgsb-box%2Froute-download%2F618926%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20report%20from%20the%20Stanford%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20the%20money%20that's%20gone%20to%20private%20equity%20firms.%20They%20have%20generated%20about%20%249.8%20billion%20for%20investors%20and%20%242.4%20billion%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%20per%20Stanford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they're%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20popular%20career%20choice%3A%20Until%202013%2C%20fewer%20than%2010%20funds%20were%20launched%20per%20year%2C%20on%20average%2C%20according%20to%20Stanford's%20report.%20But%20by%202020%2C%2066%20such%20funds%20hit%20the%20market.%20A%20third%20of%20%26quot%3Bsearchers%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Stanford%20termed%20the%20fund%20founders%2C%20took%20a%20recent%20business%20school%20class%20about%20entrepreneurship%20through%20acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20search%20funds%20are%20like%20a%20mini%20version%20of%20private%20equity%3A%20They%20target%20small%20companies%2C%20often%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20employees%20that%20serve%20regional%20markets%2C%20and%20can%20own%20several%20businesses.%20Investors%20typically%20mentor%20the%20searcher%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20he%20raised%20%24600%2C000%20from%20investors%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20an%20amount%20he%20can%20spend%20at%20his%20discretion%20to%20pay%20his%20salary%2C%20business%20travel%2C%20and%20company%20expenses.%20That's%20above%20the%20median%20of%20%24425%2C000%20per%20person%20raised%20in%20Stanford's%20survey%20of%20searchers%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20fund%20is%20backed%20by%20a%20dozen%20investors%2C%20including%20search%20fund-specific%20investors%20and%20private%20equity%20firms%20he%20pitched.%20He's%20in%20talks%20to%20buy%20two%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExit%20strategies%20can%20include%20selling%20the%20revamped%20company%20to%20a%20bigger%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20going%20public%2C%20or%20buying%20out%20the%20initial%20investors%20and%20continuing%20to%20run%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Singh%2C%20running%20a%20search%20fund%20means%20making%20less%20money%20in%20the%20short-term%20than%20his%20HBS%20classmates%20who%20work%20in%20consulting%20or%20private%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20you%20do%20this%20job%20is%20that%20when%20you%20make%20a%20sale%2C%20you%20probably%20get%20%245%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20selling%20one%20of%20his%20acquisitions%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20reasons%20why%20he%20decided%20on%20a%20search%20fund%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22782dc869-23ea-4dea-951d-8c082a8b64f7%5C%22%3EShift%20in%20the%20search%20fund%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222243%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20Singh%20outside%20Harvard%20Business%20School%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665433d9a961b37edf3a1d44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESingh%20graduated%20from%20Harvard's%20MBA%20program%20in%202022.%3Cp%3EGaurav%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20funds%20stereotypically%20pick%20up%20small%20HVAC%20companies%20in%20the%20Midwest%2C%20not%20tech%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20tech%20people%20have%20stayed%20away%20from%20search%20funds%20because%20it's%20not%20exciting%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20people%20have%20started%20to%20love%20software%20within%20the%20search%20fund%20space%20because%20it%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20to%20find%20legacy%20software%20businesses%20that%20could%20benefit%20from%20a%20new%20or%20more%20efficient%20business%20model%2C%20he%20said.%20These%20could%20be%20projects%20that%20convert%20on-premise%20software%20companies%20to%20cloud%20companies%20or%20projects%20that%20change%20one-time%20software%20purchases%20to%20yearly%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293404864-09aa-4b63-a532-bf3d50a1060b%5C%22%3EGenerational%20transfer%20opportunities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20small%20companies%20do%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-create-business-succession-plan-step-down-ceo-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccession%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20may%20fold%20if%20they%20are%20not%20acquired%2C%20giving%20search%20funds%20a%20good%20pitch%20for%20buying%20them%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-retiring-soon-ready-to-do-all-the-things-2024-5%5C%22%