2%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6653df56239fda2da6cbdc04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20of%20University%20of%20Chicago%20researchers%20investigated%20GPT's%20ability%20to%20analyze%20financial%20statements.%3Cp%3ERafael%20Henrique%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20group%20of%20researchers%20asked%20whether%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20could%20effectively%20perform%20financial%20analysis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20tool%20could%20perform%20better%20than%20a%20human.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGPT-4%20performed%20better%20at%20financial%20analysis%20with%20larger%2C%20more%20mature%20firms%2C%20researchers%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20found%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-launch-better-gpt-5-chatbot-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20perform%20financial%20statement%20analysis%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20predict%20a%20company's%20future%20performance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20than%20a%20human%20analyst%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20researchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20Booth%20School%20of%20Business%20%E2%80%94%20Alex%20Kim%2C%20Maximilian%20Muhn%2C%20and%20Valeri%20Nikolaev%20%E2%80%94%20conducted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4835311%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-lazy-again-users-defecting-rivals-anthropic-claude-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecould%20analyze%20financial%20statements%20purely%20with%20numbers%2C%20meaning%20the%20researchers%20didn't%20provide%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-rare-breed-of-huge-ai-model-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20any%20textual%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20didn't%20include%20text%20typically%20accompanied%20in%20quarterly%20earnings%20reports%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Management%20Discussion%20and%20Analysis%20(MD%26amp%3BA)%20section%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20textual%20information%20is%20easy%20to%20integrate%2C%20our%20primary%20interest%20lies%20in%20understanding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELLMs'%3C%2Fa%3E%20ability%20to%20analyze%20and%20synthesize%20purely%20financial%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20examined%20over%20150%2C000%20firm-year%20observations%20%E2%80%94%20or%20data%20collected%20on%20a%20firm%20in%20one%20year%20%E2%80%94%20from%20about%2015%2C000%20companies%20between%201968%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-giants-openai-anthropic-running-out-of-good-training-data-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Muhn%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20could%20grade%20how%20financial%20analysts%20performed%20in%20their%20forecasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20analysts%20achieved%20a%2053%25%20accuracy%20in%20one-month%20forecasts%20of%20the%20direction%20of%20future%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20study%2C%20the%20researchers%20then%20fed%20GPT-4%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efinancial%20statements%20without%20any%20textual%20information%20and%20anonymized%20the%20data%20so%20that%20the%20model%20wouldn't%20know%20which%20companies'%20data%20it%20was%20analyzing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20GPT%20was%20given%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimple%26quot%3B%20prompt%20that%20does%20not%20use%20%26quot%3Bchain-of-thought%20command%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20researchers%20asked%20the%20model%20to%20answer%20without%20breaking%20up%20the%20request%20into%20step-by-step%20instructions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20model%20scored%20slightly%20worse%20than%20analysts%20with%20a%2052%25%20accuracy%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20model's%20performance%20changed%20when%20the%20researchers%20used%20a%20chain-of-thought%20command%20prompt.%20According%20to%20the%20study%2C%20by%20giving%20GPT%20more%20instruction%20and%20guidance%2C%20the%20model%20achieved%20a%2060%25%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20that%20when%20GPT%20is%20given%20more%20instruction%2C%20approaching%20analysis%20like%20a%20human%2C%20the%20model%20%26quot%3Bcan%20outperform%20human%20analysts%26quot%3B%20even%20without%20key%20text%20information%20typically%20found%20in%20financial%20reports%2C%20the%20study%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20noted%20in%20their%20study%20that%20financial%20analysis%20and%20prediction%20are%20highly%20complex%20tasks%20that%20require%20judgment%2C%20common%20sense%2C%20and%20intuition%2C%20which%20can%20stump%20humans%20and%20machines.%20This%20may%20explain%20why%20neither%20group%20is%20churning%20out%20anything%20near%20100%25%20accuracy%20in%20their%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293e47370-01b8-4757-8009-fd1379eafba3%5C%22%3EWill%20analysts%20be%20replaced%20by%20AI%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20anecdotal%20observation%20Muhn%20noted%20to%20BI%20that%20is%20not%20shown%20in%20the%20study%20is%20that%20GPT%20appeared%20to%20be%20better%20at%20analyzing%20larger%20companies.%20Think%20places%20like%20Apple%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20larger%20firms%20like%20Apple%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20do%20relatively%20better%2C%20which%20could%20be%20related%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20generally%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20shown%20in%20prior%20literature%20%E2%80%94%20larger%20firms%20or%20more%20mature%20firms%20are%20essentially%20less%20idiosyncratic%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20small%20biotech%20firm%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20company's%20profitability%20in%20the%20next%20year%20can%20be%20highly%20variable%20on%20factors%20like%20a%20successful%20clinical%20trial%2C%20the%20researcher%20said%2C%20making%20prediction%20harder%20for%20GPT%20based%20solely%20on%20financial%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20noted%20that%20GPT-4%20could%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20analysis%20since%20humans%20can%20be%20biased%20in%20cases%20like%20incorporating%20information%20rationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20acknowledged%20to%20BI%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-acting-weird-ai-researcher-says-users-could-be-blame-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELLMs%20also%20have%20biases%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20defining%20biases%20can%20be%20tricky%2C%20he%20said%2C%20since%20people%20can%20be%20talking%20about%20political%20biases%20in%20a%20model%20or%20a%20positive%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20the%20LLM%20had%20a%20very%20strong%20bias%20in%20making%20some%20earnings-related%20predictions%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20very%20bad%20in%20predicting%20the%20outcomes%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20seems%20like%20it's%20doing%2C%20on%20average%2C%20pretty%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fortunebusinessinsights.com%2Ffinancial-analytics-market-107948%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultibillion-dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20question%3A%20Can%20LLMs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ereplace%20human%20financial%20analysts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20moment%2C%20I%20would%20say%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20complimentary.%20The%20technology%20is%20going%20to%20develop%20over%20time%2C%20and%20then%2C%20who%20knows%3F%20Two%20years%20before%2C%20we%20didn't%20even%20think%20about%20this%20kind%20of%20technology%20coming%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20emphasized%20that%20the%20research%20doesn't%20suggest%20that%20analysts%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20machines%20and%20that%2C%20for%20now%2C%20there%20are%20areas%20where%20human%20experts%20can%20do%20better%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20research%20provides%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20tools%20that%20may%20soon%20be%20available%20to%20a%20financial%20analyst%20to%20determine%20a%20company's%20health%20more%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20Apple%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4-predict-company-future-performance-better-than-humans-study-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717370903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6653df7ea961b37edf3a1a63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4-predict-company-future-performance-better-than-humans-study-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20University%20of%20Chicago%20researchers%20found%20that%20GPT-4%20outperformed%20human%20financial%20analysts%20even%20without%20any%20textual%20information.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4-predict-company-future-performance-better-than-humans-study-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K