target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMailOnline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sisters%2C%20whose%20father%20is%20the%20Palestinian%20real-estate%20developer%20Mohamed%20Anwar%20Hadid%2C%20have%20previously%20voiced%20their%20support%20for%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sisters%20are%20among%20the%20most%20high-profile%20celebrity%20supporters%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israel%2C%20Gigi%2C%2029%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgigi-hadid-condemns-terrorizing-innocent-people-following-hamas-attacks-palestine-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20a%20statement%20on%20Instagram%20that%20got%20millions%20of%20likes%2C%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20thoughts%20are%20with%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20this%20unjustifiable%20tragedy%2C%20and%20every%20day%20that%20innocent%20lives%20are%20taken%20by%20this%20conflict%20-%20too%20many%20of%20which%20are%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20deep%20empathy%20and%20heartbreak%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20struggle%20and%20life%20under%20occupation%2C%20it's%20a%20responsibility%20I%20hold%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20have%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20none%20of%20them%20include%20the%20harm%20of%20a%20Jewish%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Bella%2C%2027%2C%20wrote%20on%20Instagram%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bdevastated%20at%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20empathy%20coming%20from%20the%20government%20systems%20worldwide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20says%20in%20the%20post%20that%20she%20is%20the%20child%20of%20a%20Nakba%20survivor.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fabout-the-nakba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nakba%20means%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe%26quot%3B%20in%20Arabic%20and%20is%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mass%20displacement%20and%20dispossession%20of%20Palestinians%20during%20the%201948%20Arab-Israeli%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBella%20was%20also%20recently%20seen%20at%20the%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20wearing%20a%20dress%20resembling%20the%20Palestinian%20keffiyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMohamed%20Hadid%20has%20also%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmohamedhadid%2Fp%2FC7sY9WSP7ij%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20to%20make%20his%20position%20on%20the%20conflict%20clear%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20called%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bthe%20butcher%20of%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%20vote%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CANNES%2C%20FRANCE%20-%20MAY%2023%3A%20Bella%20Hadid%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20croisette%20during%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20on%20May%2023%2C%202024%20in%20Cannes%2C%20France.%20(Photo%20by%20Arnold%20Jerocki%2FGC%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665c7abdcc442a2f676d060f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBella%20Hadid%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20croisette%20during%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20on%20May%2023%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EArnold%20Jerocki%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20donations%20follow%20a%20major%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20the%20southern%20Gazan%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%2045%20people%20in%20a%20tent%20camp%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%2C%20prompting%20global%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2024%2F05%2F31%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-on-the-middle-east-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20three-phase%20proposal%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20calls%20for%20a%20cease-fire%2C%20an%20exchange%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20and%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20from%20populated%20areas%20of%20Gaza%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20protesters%20gathered%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20demanding%20Israel's%20leaders%20accept%20the%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttendees%20of%20the%20Tel%20Aviv%20demonstration%20said%20that%20the%20protest%20was%20the%20largest%20since%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fsome-120000-anti-government-protesters-rally-in-tel-aviv-14-officers-said-hurt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Roughly%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Israel%20during%20the%20attacks%2C%20and%20around%20a%20further%20240%20were%20taken%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2036%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20died%20in%20the%20following%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20the%20territory's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgigi-bella-hadid-donate-1-million-aid-gaza-palestinians-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717349214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665c85b51cd3b17790425e49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgigi-bella-hadid-donate-1-million-aid-gaza-palestinians-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sisters%2C%20whose%20father%20is%20the%20Palestinian%20real-estate%20developer%20Mohamed%20Anwar%20Hadid%2C%20have%20previously%20voiced%20their%20support%20for%20Gazans.%22%2C%22