igcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Suhas%E2%80%99%20grandparents%20made%20icecreams%20when%20he%20was%20a%20kid.%20%E2%80%9CAlmost%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20they%20had%20a%20small%20local%20icecream%20business.%20My%20inspiration%20also%20comes%20from%20them.%20Initially%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20their%20recipes%20and%20knowledge%20to%20start%20my%20manufacturing%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20main%20ingredient%20used%20in%20making%20icecream%20available%20to%20him%20in%20abundance%20and%20his%20grandparents%E2%80%99%20recipes%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20open%20a%20small%20outlet%20and%20shop%20in%20Nellore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20made%2045%20litres%20of%20icecream%20and%20within%20two%20days%20of%20opening%20the%20store%2C%20the%20icecreams%20were%20sold%20out.%20The%20sales%20were%20quite%20organic%3B%20word%20spread%20around%20the%20town%20and%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20visiting%20the%20shop.%20I%20had%20to%20close%20my%20shop%20for%20one%20day%20and%20increase%20production.%20On%20the%20fifth%20day%2C%20we%20came%20with%20double%20the%20stock%20and%20have%20never%20looked%20back%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20making%20great%20sales%20and%20opened%20another%20shop%20in%20Nellore.%20Within%20three%20years%2C%20I%20have%20established%20more%20than%2015%20stores%20across%20South%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20quick%20to%20get%20into%20the%20B2B%20business%20of%20franchising%20his%20icecream%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20the%20company%20makes%20six%20to%20seven%20lakh%20litres%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345217%2Fbest-ice-cream-parlours-places-mumbai-snowman-taj-icecream-haji-ali-gokul-rustom-naturals-bachelorr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eicecream%20every%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E