0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%20is%20a%20competitive%20and%20demanding%20profession%20which%20requires%20one%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20reading%20and%20documentation.%20The%20general%20understanding%20so%20far%20has%20been%20that%20this%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20a%20visually-impaired%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20digital%20innovations%20have%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20add%20to%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20profession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201021px)%20100vw%2C%201021px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221021%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anchal%20Bhateja's%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034.jpeg%201021w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-239x300.jpeg%20239w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-500x627.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-768x963.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-27-at-4.27.44-PM-1716887034-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351293%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnchal%20Bhateja%E2%80%99s%20journey%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20widespread%20accessibility%20awareness.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInclusivity%20IRL%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20disability%20inclusion%20journey%20at%20her%20organisation%2C%20Seema%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20human%20resources%20manager%20based%20out%20of%20Delhi%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CIncluding%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20has%20helped%20the%20organisation%20in%20several%20unintended%20ways.%20Beyond%20just%20creating%20a%20more%20equitable%20workforce%2C%20having%20PwDs%20at%20the%20workplace%20has%20helped%20us%20relook%20at%20our%20policies%2C%20processes%20and%20infrastructure%20from%20a%20new%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20employers%20warm%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20employing%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20also%20moving%20towards%20becoming%20a%20more%20inclusive%20space%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20this%20sentiment%2C%20Amar%20Jain%2C%20a%20visually%20impaired%20lawyer%20and%20accessibility%20professional%2C%20says%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20lawyer%20with%20a%20disability%2C%20we%20face%20enormous%20barriers.%20The%20data%20provided%20by%20clients%20is%20not%20accessible%2C%20the%20physical%20case%20files%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20digital%20copies.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20progressive%20steps%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20judicial%20system.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20recently%20released%20a%20mandate%20to%20provide%20digital%20copies%20of%20case%20files%20to%20lawyers%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20landscape%20is%20changing%2C%20slowly%20but%20surely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20understanding%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%20Anchal%20interned%20at%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20chambers%20as%20a%20student.%20She%20remembers%20how%20forthcoming%20they%20were%20with%20respect%20to%20offering%20%E2%80%98Reasonable%20Accommodations%E2%80%99%20to%20help%20her%20work%20be