.%20Captivated%20by%20its%20deliciousness%2C%20Sandeep%20was%20inspired%20to%20share%20this%20culinary%20delight%20with%20his%20city.%20Within%20a%20few%20short%20months%2C%20his%20dream%20became%20a%20reality%20as%20he%20opened%20the%20inaugural%20Pizza%20Galleria%20outlet%20in%20December%202015%2C%20right%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Gohana%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293491%2Fpunjab-man-starts-pizza-truck-earns-lakhs-learns-from-ranveer-brar-youtube-videos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epizza%20chain%20%3C%2Fa%3Eapart%20from%20others%20is%20that%20it%20is%20100%20percent%20vegetarian%2C%20and%20has%20pizzas%20starting%20from%20Rs%2069.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20turning%20the%20people%20of%20Gohana%20into%20pizza%20lovers%2C%20Sandeep%20started%20opening%20outlets%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Haryana%2C%20and%20soon%20expanded%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20over%2072%20outlets%20that%20sell%20over%2020%2C000%20pizzas%20every%20day%2C%20with%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2015%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20this%2032-year-old%20went%20from%20having%20arrears%20in%20his%20engineering%20course%20to%20being%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%2C%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%20700%20people!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20a%20city%20to%20the%20taste%20of%20pizza%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20in%20Gohana%20where%20his%20father%20managed%20a%20construction%20material%20business%20%E2%80%94%20a%20setting%20that%20ignited%20his%20early%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%20Following%20his%20schooling%2C%20he%20studied%20at%20NC%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Israna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20da