his%20first%20bite%20of%20pizza%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20which%20changed%20his%20life%20forever.%20%E2%80%9CI%20loved%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20pizza%20and%20wondered%20how%20it%20was%20made.%20It%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20fatter%20version%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20sauce%20and%20cheese%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20food%20business%20crept%20into%20his%20mind.%20But%20how%20does%20one%20make%20a%20pizza%20and%20build%20a%20business%20around%20the%20same%3F%20To%20learn%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20such%20a%20business%2C%20he%20approached%20a%20few%20pizza%20outlets%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20Haryana.%20It%20was%20Pizza%20Wings%20in%20Rohtak%20where%20he%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20learn%20the%20ABCs%20of%20running%20a%20pizza%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20trained%20for%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20at%20Pizza%20Wings.%20They%20taught%20me%20everything%20from%20how%20to%20make%20the%20dough%20and%20the%20sauce%20to%20how%20to%20deliver%20the%20pizza%20and%20run%20a%20store.%20I%20realised%20that%20making%20a%20pizza%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20completing%20his%20training%2C%20Sandeep%20returned%20home%20and%20shared%20his%20ambitious%20business%20plan%20with%20his%20family%20%E2%80%94%20opening%20a%20pizza%20shop%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20centre.%20However%2C%20his%20father%20was%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20venture.%20Undeterred%2C%20Sandeep%20sought%20support%20from%20his%20brother%20and%20friends%2C%20who%20collectively%20contributed%20the%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%206.5%20lakh%20to%20establish%20his%20inaugural%20store%20in%20Gohana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC61bd2stDl0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Pizza%20Galleria%20(%40pizzagalleria_india)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20upset%20about%20me%20quitting%20and%20returning.%20He%20expected%20me%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20myself%20as%20an%20engineer%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandeep.%20While%20convincing%20his%20family%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20finding%20skilled%20labour%20for%20the%20store%20in%20a%20city%20where%20many%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20tasted%20a%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hired%20three%20boys%20who%20had%20completed%20Class%2012%20and%20trusted%20my%20vision.%20I%20taught%20them%20how%20to%20make%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249937%2Fgujarat-ahmedabad-jashuben-shah-old-pizza-best-food-dominos