began%20the%20journey%20of%20sun%20drying%2C%20optimising%20the%20hygiene%20quotient%20and%20teaching%20the%20locals%20to%20market%20the%20fruit%20to%20customers%20using%20words%20like%20%E2%80%98organic%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98solar%20dried%E2%80%99.%20Currently%2C%20the%20fruit%20retails%20for%20Rs%20465.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20nudged%20the%20women%20farmers%20to%20explore%20other%20crops%2C%20like%20soybeans%20and%20oyster%20mushrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20saw%20these%20alternatives%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205675%2Findia-women-anaemia-iron-deficiency-symptom-causes-treatment-doctor-low-haemoglobin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepidemic%20of%20anaemia%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20grapples%20the%20Ladakh%20region.%20Through%20these%20initiatives%2C%20Takmachik%20became%20an%20eco-village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20first%20eco-village%20of%20Ladakh%20was%20seeing%20results%20with%20its%20eco-friendly%20practices%2C%20Upadhyaya%20was%20flooded%20with%20requests%20to%20replicate%20the%20model%20in%20the%20other%20villages%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20morning%20settles%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20birds%E2%80%99%20banter%20can%20be%20distinctly%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpadhyaya%20is%20grateful%20for%20these%20%E2%80%98better%E2%80%99%20days.%20The%20horrors%20of%20watching%20entire%20families%20and%20homes%20being%20wiped%20out%2C%20not%20just%20once%20in%20the%20flash%20floods%20of%202010%20but%20in%20all%20the%20others%20that%20followed%2C%20is%20a%20fresh%20memory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20days%20I%20have%20hugged%20the%20villagers%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20we%20would%20come%20out%20of%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274165%2Ftop-inspiring-